      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1612 - Ya'qub ibn Shu'ayb asked him (Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as)) about the tithes collected from a man: \"Can they be counted as part of his Zakat?\"\nImam (as) replied: \"Yes, if he wishes.\""
